               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Hydroxyzine Hydrochloride Tablets, USP:</paragraph>
                  <table width="431.000" ID="id_c18f4c60-3e30-4b3d-be99-39af31e75c8c">
